  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Investigation of changes in gray and white matter during immoblisation after injury of the
      right upper extremity via two MR Investigations of the brain at two different times.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Investigation of changes in gray and white matter during immoblisation after injury of the
      right upper extremity via two MR Investigations of the brain at two different times.
      Immobilisation at least 12 days. Time between the 2 investigations: 12-14 d.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
